  • メソッドの詳細

    • getBlock

      Block getBlock​(int x, int y, int z)
      Get a block at the specified position
      パラメータ:
      x - the x coordinate of the block
      y - the y coordinate of the block
      z - the z coordinate of the block
      戻り値:
      block at the specified position

    • setBlock

      void setBlock​(int x, int y, int z, Block block, boolean physics)
      Set a block at the specified position
      パラメータ:
      x - the x coordinate of the block
      y - the y coordinate of the block
      z - the z coordinate of the block
      block - to place
      physics - whether apply physics when setting a block
      例外:
      IllegalArgumentException - if the world cannot set the block

    • spawnParticle

      void spawnParticle​(double x, double y, double z, Particle particle, int count)
      Spawn particle(s) at the specified position
      パラメータ:
      x - the x coordinate of the block
      y - the y coordinate of the block
      z - the z coordinate of the block
      particle - to spawn
      例外:
      IllegalArgumentException - if this world can not spawn the particle
